title: PRADA
seo_description: Italian designer Miuccia Prada revolutionized the world of luxury goods with the launch of her nylon bags line. Her designs combine unconventional color schemes, unlikely pairings and careful attention to detail – right down to the buttons on each blouse.

Italian designer Miuccia Prada revolutionized the world of luxury goods with the launch of her nylon bags line. Her designs combine unconventional color schemes, unlikely pairings and careful attention to detail – right down to the buttons on each blouse.
